To solve this, we first condense the product as follows:For $x,y\in\mathbb{R}^+$,note \begin{align*}
\left(x+\frac1y\right)\left(x+\frac1y-2018\right)=-2018x-\frac{2018}{y}+x^2+\frac1{y^2}=-2018\left(x+\frac1y\right)+x^2+\frac1{y^2}.
\end{align*}Using the Arithmetic Mean-Geometric Mean Inequality, we get $x^2+\frac1{y^2}\ge2x\cdot\frac1y=\frac{2x}{y}$. We also have $2x+\frac2y\ge4\sqrt{x\cdot\frac1y}=\frac{4\sqrt2\sqrt x}{\sqrt y}\ge4\sqrt2\left(\frac{x+y}2\right)=2\sqrt2\left(x+\frac1y\right)$. Therefore, \begin{align*}
-2018\left(x+\frac1y\right)+x^2+\frac1{y^2}&\ge-2018\left(x+\frac1y\right)+2x\cdot\frac1y\\&=-2017\left(x+\frac1y\right).
\end{align*}<answer>Thus, \begin{align*}
\left(x+\frac1y\right)\left(x+\frac1y-2018\right)+\left(y+\frac1x\right)\left(y+\frac1x-2018\right)&=-2017\left(x+\frac1y\right)-2017\left(y+\frac1x\right)\\&\ge-2017\cdot2\sqrt{xy\cdot\frac{xy}{1008014}}\\&=-4034\sqrt{\frac3{1008014}}.
\end{align*}($\text{Equality}$ occurs $\Leftrightarrow x=y=3x^2\Rightarrow x=y=\sqrt{\frac3{1008014}}$. So, $\text{minimum value}=-4034\sqrt{\frac3{1008014}}$.</answer>

Now, $5\sqrt{1+x}$ and $5\sqrt{1-x}$ are positive homogenous expressions of degree $\frac{1}{2}$, and their coefficients are also positive homogenous expressions of degree $\frac{1}{2}$ so by homogenization we can set $x=\frac{y^2}{1-y^2}$, where $y$ is an indeterminate. Then we have</think>
\begin{align*}&5\sqrt{1+\frac{y^2}{1-y^2}}+5\sqrt{1-\frac{y^2}{1-y^2}}=7\sqrt{2}\\ &\Leftrightarrow 5\sqrt{\frac{1-y^2+y^2}{1-y^2}}+5\sqrt{\frac{1-y^2-y^2}{1-y^2}}=7\sqrt{2}\\ &\Leftrightarrow 5\sqrt{\frac{1}{1-y^2}}+5\sqrt{\frac{1-2y^2}{1-y^2}}=7\sqrt{2} \end{align*}
<answer>$y=\frac{\sqrt{2}}{2}$. Thus, $x=\frac{y^2}{1-y^2}=\boxed{\frac{1}{2}}$</answer>

problem:
The graph of the equation $y = \frac{x}{x^3 + Ax^2 + Bx + C}$, where $A,B,C$ are integers, is shown below. Find $A + B + C$. [asy]
import graph; size(8.14cm); real lsf=0.5; pen dps=linewidth(0.7)+fontsize(10); defaultpen(dps); pen ds=black; real xmin=-3.52,xmax=4.62,ymin=-3.66,ymax=3.94;

pen cqcqcq=rgb(0.75,0.75,0.75);

/*grid*/ pen gs=linewidth(0.7)+cqcqcq+linetype("2 2"); real gx=1,gy=1;
for(real i=ceil(xmin/gx)*gx;i<=floor(xmax/gx)*gx;i+=gx) draw((i,ymin)--(i,ymax),gs); for(real i=ceil(ymin/gy)*gy;i<=floor(ymax/gy)*gy;i+=gy) draw((xmin,i)--(xmax,i),gs);

Label laxis; laxis.p=fontsize(10);

xaxis("$x$",xmin,xmax,Ticks(laxis,Step=1.0,Size=2,NoZero),Arrows(6),above=true); yaxis("$y$",ymin,ymax,Ticks(laxis,Step=1.0,Size=2,NoZero),Arrows(6),above=true); real f1(real x){return x/((x-1)*(x-2)*(x+2));} draw(graph(f1,-3.51,-2.01),linewidth(1.2)); draw(graph(f1,-1.99,0.99),linewidth(1.2)); draw(graph(f1,1.01,1.99),linewidth(1.2)); draw(graph(f1,2.01,4.61),linewidth(1.2));

clip((xmin,ymin)--(xmin,ymax)--(xmax,ymax)--(xmax,ymin)--cycle);

[/asy]

